text: Kyra Lillee Cooney-Cross (born 15 February 2002) is an Australian soccer player. She plays for Arsenal W.F.C. in the Women's Super League and for the Australia women's national soccer team (nicknamed the "Matildas"). ==References== Category:2002 births Category:Living people Category:Australian women's soccer players Category:Soccer players from Brisbane
